.TH plfs_get_filetype 3 "${PACKAGE_STRING}" 
.SH NAME
plfs_get_filetype 
.SH SYNTAX
#include <plfs.h>
.PP
plfs_filetype plfs_get_filetype( const char *path );

.SH DESCRIPTION
This is needed for MPI/IO to know to avoid optimizations unless
the file is a container type file (workload of shared_file or n-1).

.SH INPUT PARAMETERS
.TP 1i
path
the name of the file to check its type.


.SH RETURN VALUES
Returns one of the enumerations of plfs_filetype. These are:
CONTAINER, FLAT_FILE, SMALL_FILE, and PFT_UNKNOWN.

